Description: A text value for the record (e.g. Moneyline; Player Prop; 3rd Quarter)

Name: BettingBetTypes
Description: A list of the possible BettingBetTypes (e.g. Moneyline; Spread)

Name: BettingMarketTypes
Description: A list of the possible BettingMartketTypes (e.g. Game Line; Team Prop)

Name: BettingPeriodTypes
Description: A list of the possible BettingPeriodTypes (e.g. Full Game; Regulation Time; 1st Half)

Name: BettingEventTypes
Description: A list of the possible BettingEventTypes (e.g. Game; Future)

Name: BettingOutcomeTypes
Description: A list of the possible BettingOutcomeTypes (e.g. Home; Over)

Name: ResultedMarketMetaData
Description: A list of the combinations of BettingMarketTypeID; BettingBetTypeID; and BettingPeriodTypeID that will be resulted

Name: BettingResultTypes
Description: A list of the possible BettingResultTypes (e.g. Win; Loss; Push)

Name: GameID
Description: The unique id of the game record

Name: SeasonType
Description: The seasontype of the score

Name: Season
Description: The season of the score

Name: Week
Description: The week of the score

Name: Day
Description: The start time of the score

Name: AwayTeam

Name: HomeTeam
Description: The home team key

Name: BettingMarketTypeID

Name: BettingMarketType
